(169, 1392707611, '', 'Hudson () ', 'Management', 'Beijing, China', 'China', 'Beijing', 'Beijing', 39.904030, 116.407524, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>Hudson () 25</p>\n<h4>Fast Track Promotion!; Fun &amp; Dynamic Working Environment; Annual Package Plus Quarterly Bonus Scheme</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;Fast track your career</li>\n<li>&nbsp;World class training, by experienced professionals</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Fun, dynmic, challenging, rewarding</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hudson is a global talent solutions company with a strong presence in the Asia Pacific region. We are growing our business in Asia and hence are recruiting Associate Consultants within our Management Trainee Program in Hong Kong.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our 25 week program provides you with step by step world class theory and on the job training on how to be a successful recruitment consultant.&nbsp;&nbsp;In line with our philosophy of transparency and meritocracy, how soon you are promoted to a Consultant role will depend solely on your performance on this program.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to start your career with a leading multinational company?</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to be trained on how to be a world class recruitment consultant?</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to get promoted based on merit and not on years of experience?</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to build and lead a team in the near future?</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Do you want to work in an environment that pushes you to achieve your potential and recognises you for your achievements?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If your answer is&nbsp;<strong>&ldquo;Yes&rdquo;,&nbsp;</strong>then<strong>&nbsp;</strong>we at Hudson are interested in talking with you. We are looking for highly motivated graduates with up to 2 years experience and a track record of excellence who want to be the best and have the drive, energy and commitment to succeed in this rewarding industry.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Invest in your career by applying today.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>CONTACT INFORMATION</h3>\n<p>Luro, Bryan<br />+861065641863<br />Hudson<br />Unit 408,North Tower, Beijing Kerry Centre, 1 Guang Hua Road, Chaoyang District<br />100020 Beijing<br />China</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'http://www.linkedin.com/jobs2/view/11262147', '', 5, 107, 2),
