(227, 1394064796, 'Siri', 'Apple', 'Language', '', 'United States', 'California', 'Cupertino', 0.000000, 0.000000, 'United States', 'California', 'Cupertino', 'H1B', 'Full Time', '<div id="job">\n<h2 id="title-29709208">Mainland Mandarin Chinese Siri Writer / Editor</h2>\n<ul class="sosumi">\n<li>Job Number: 29709208</li>\n<li title="Santa Clara Valley, California, United States">Santa Clara Valley, California, United States</li>\n<li>Posted: Feb. 27, 2014</li>\n<li>Weekly Hours: 40.00</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Job Summary</h3>\n<p class="preline">We''re looking for a creative individual who is also a native speaker of Mainland Mandarin Chinese to help us evolve and enrich Siri, Apple&rsquo;s virtual personal assistant, for our Chinese market. The ideal candidate is someone who is keenly aware of Chinese culture, loves language, and has the writing ability needed to craft and customize culturally appropriate dialog for China.</p>\n<div class="callout">\n<h3>Key Qualifications</h3>\n<ul class="square">\n<li>Current and direct exposure to <strong>Chinese</strong> culture over a sustained time period</li>\n<li>Excellent writing skills</li>\n<li>Great vocabulary and <strong>Chinese</strong> cultural knowledge</li>\n<li>Demonstrated experience writing character-driven dialog</li>\n<li>Demonstrated ability to elicit and synthesize ideas from a variety of creative sources</li>\n<li>Excellent technical and grammatical language skills</li>\n<li>Proficiency in English; translation experience is a plus</li>\n<li>Demonstrated multi-disciplinary teamwork skills</li>\n<li>Experience with user-centered design and consumer software is a plus</li>\n<li>Additionally, experience writing for advertising, marketing, television, or radio is a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h3>Description</h3>\n<p class="preline">Assess the Siri dialogs and identify opportunities for cultural enhancements Develop and write original dialog to support Siri capabilities Help evolve Siri as a distinct, recognizable character Ensure consistency and quality of Siri dialog from all sources Work closely with language engineering, translation, and development teams.</p>\n<h3>Education</h3>\n<p class="preline">B.A./B.S. or equivalent</p>\n<h2 class="preline">apple!</h2>\n</div>', 'https://jobs.apple.com/us/search?job=29709208&openJobId=29709208&board_id=17682#&openJobId=29709208', '', 5, 262, 2),
