(234, 1394492595, '', 'Red Bull', 'Media', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.714352, -74.005974, '', '', '', 'None', 'Internship', '<div class="WB_text">NYRed Bulldigitla marketingbrand marketingPlus</div>\n<div class="WB_text">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class="WB_text">\n<div class="l-1-6">\n<p class="f-leader">In 1987, Red Bull not only launched a completely new product, it created and has lead ever since a whole new product category, Energy Drinks. Nowadays Red Bull employs more than 8000 people in over 165 countries, selling over 5 billion cans a year. The World of Red Bull provides the forum for you to use your talent and passion, to develop yourself and make an impact. Find out why we''re different.</p>\n<p>Red Bull is looking for a team of interns to join the Brand Marketing, Digital Marketing, Distribution and On-Premise teams this summer in New York City. These internships will provide unique opportunities to gain hands-on capability and insight into the daily operations of growing a global brand. Responsibilities will vary, but at the end of the day this experience is what you make of it.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="l-1-6">\n<div class="f-headingCombo">\n<h2 class="f-h1">Your experience includes:</h2>\n<h3 class="f-h2">(proven performance in)</h3>\n</div>\n<ol class="qualiList">\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>Actively enrolled in a four-year college/university</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>A doer with a track record of accomplishment</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>A history of managing complex projects, and a knack for balancing priorities</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>A passionate leader who inspires others to achieve big things</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>Strong interpersonal skills and ability to work effectively with people of all levels; team player</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>Strong verbal and written communication skills</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>Demonstrated ability to effectively manage multiple projects and prioritize work</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>Ability to work independently in a high energy and fast paced environment</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>Inspired to learn while doing and a winning, can-do attitude</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>Affinity for the Red Bull values: Professional, Focused, Responsible, Passionate - and humble too</p>\n</li>\n<li class="qualiList__item">\n<p>Live and represent the Red Bull brand: demonstrated passion for life</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class="tip-box">\n<p class="f-leader">In your cover letter, please include an explanation of why your experience is specifically relevant to this role at Red Bull. We want to see your personal style &ndash; what makes you tick and why you think your next opportunity is here with us.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'http://jobs.redbull.com/us/en/summer-internship-program-new-york-009536', '', 5, 142, 2),
