(292, 1395785923, 'Communication/Marketing Coordinator/Business Development', 'MAD Architects', 'Design', '', 'United States', 'California', 'Santa Monica', 0.000000, 0.000000, 'United States', 'California', 'Santa Monica', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>MAD602011MADFASTCOMPANY10</p>\n<p>MAD Los Angeles office is currently seeking Communication/Marketing Coordinator/ Business Development&nbsp;<br /><br />Applicants must demonstrate the following qualities:&nbsp;<br />&bull; a strong educational background in Marketing /PR/Communications or a relevant major.&nbsp;<br />&bull; A minimum of four years&rsquo; experience in marketing /Press/Communication in major international architecture firms or a relevant profession with professional experience in art promotion.&nbsp;<br />&bull; Fluent English in spoken and written, great writing skill especially, with experience working/studying internationally (Chinese and English speaker is preferred. Tri-lingual is preferred)&nbsp;<br />&bull; understanding the core function of architect firm, and major communication and marketing functions, how to operate them.&nbsp;<br />&bull; Solid written and verbal communication skills as well as grammatical proofing and editing abilities (familiarity with publication production or graphic design would be preferred)&nbsp;<br />&bull; a solid track record communication and marketing skills in traditional and new media&nbsp;<br />&bull; good with establish new connections and also maintain the exist connections.&nbsp;<br />&bull; experience working with Word, Excel, PowerPoint and Mail/Outlook (knowledge of the Adobe Suite and database management is desirable)&nbsp;<br />&bull; a positive attitude towards obstacles and tight deadlines, out-going, strong communicator and able to take priorities and handle multi-tasks when he/she is required to do so.&nbsp;<br /><br />Main job tasks and responsibilities:&nbsp;<br />&bull; Draft or Edit press releases/project descriptions, responding to journalist re