(295, 1395871846, 'Sales Associate', 'The Finish Line Inc', 'Service', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.714352, -74.005974, '', '', '', 'None', 'Part Time', '<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Finish Line and Macy''s have partnered to create a one of a kind retail experience inside of the Macy''s footwear departments all over the country, and we are&nbsp;currently hiring for part-time&nbsp;<strong>Sales Associates</strong>&nbsp;to join our team at three new Finish Line''s in Flushing<strong>.&nbsp;</strong>It would be ideal if this Sales Associate is&nbsp;<strong>bilingual in English and Chinese/Mandarin.</strong></font></p>\n<p><font face="Verdana, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif">As a Sales Associate for Finish Line, you are a living, breathing billboard,&nbsp;a human Google search working to find the best products&nbsp;for our customers, and an ambassador of some of the world''s greatest athletic retail brands. &nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Verdana, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Sales Associates with Finish Line Receive:</font></p>\n<ul type="disc">\n<li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Competitive compensation plans</font></li>\n<li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Opportunities for additional&nbsp;incentive pay</font></li>\n<li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Employee discounts</font></li>\n<li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Opportunities for advancement and career growth!</font></li>\n</ul>', '', '2459@finishline.com', 5, 125, 2),
(296, 1395872903, 'Designer (mid-level)', 'Fuhu', 'Design', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '', '', 'Carson', 'None', 'Full Time', '<div class="jobPostings view">\n<div class="posting description">\n<p>Fuhu Inc., is the leading designer, seller and innovator of &ldquo;thoughtful&rdquo; consumer products and services for children.&nbsp; Creator of the nabi&trade; tablet, the world&rsquo;s first tablet made just for kids, Fuhu provides an ecosystem of hardware, software services, and accessories to immerse kids in rich and engaging experiences.&nbsp; nabi &trade; is available in all major U.S. retailers including Walmart, Best Buy, GameStop, and Target.<br /><br />We are currently looking for a Designer to join our growing team. If you are looking for a fast paced environment at a fast growing company, please apply!<br /><br />Duties:<br />Uses knowledge of current graphic design software to produce graphic art and visual materials for promotions, advertisements, packaging, and informative and instructional material through a variety of media outlets.<br />Must remain abreast of technological advances in the field and be able to identify areas of use in the organization.<br />Familiar with standard concepts, practices, and procedures within a particular field.<br />Relies on limited experience and judgment to plan and accomplish goals.<br />Performs a variety of tasks related to graphic design.<br />Works under general supervision; typically reports to a supervisor or manager.<br />A great deal of creativity and latitude is expected.<br />&nbsp;<br /><br />Requirements:<br />At least 3 years experience working as a Designer.<br />Advanced knowledge of Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop, and a strong grasp of design principles.<br />Deadline oriented.<br />Strong in conceptual and problem solving skills; critical thinking.<br />A portfolio or sample work that clearly communicates successful design soluti