(299, 1396034233, '', 'mom365 Newborn Photographer', 'Media', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.714352, -74.005974, '', '', '', 'None', 'Part Time', '<p >Love Babies? Love Photography? Mom365 provides a unique opportunity to earn extra income taking baby photos at your local hospital.</p>\n <p >As a Photographer-Sales Rep, you''ll work in the maternity ward of a hospital near you taking baby photos and selling packages to mom and dad. No photography experience? Don''t worry! You''ll use our equipment and we''ll provide you with photography training.</p>\n <p >We are currently seeking Photographers/Sales Reps at:<br />THE NEW YORK HOSPITAL MEDICAL CENTER QUEENS<br />Schedule: 4-5 days a week and weekends; 9am to approximate 5pm</p>\n <p >Qualifications:<br />MUST SPEAK MANDARIN/CANTONESE TO BE CONSIDERED FOR THIS POSITION<br />Strong communication and time management skills.<br />Mature, dependable, and energetic.<br />2 years of sales or customer service experience<br />Comfortable in a commission-based sales environment.<br />A passion for photography.<br />You will be expected to comply with hospital regulations regarding patient privacy, HIPPA, security, sanitation and infection control.</p>\n <p >Mom365 is the nation''s leader in hospital newborn photography. At Mom365 we strive to give every new parent the very best first portrait of his or her newborn baby and provide the level of customer service that makes our hospitals proud to be our partner. Explore an exciting part-time career opportunity with Mom365!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://jobs-mom365.icims.com/jobs/17218/bilingual-mom365-newborn-photographer---queens,-ny/job', '', 5, 140, 2),
