(315, 1396542269, 'Chinese Franchise Sales Manager ', ' Caffbene', 'Marketing', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.714352, -74.005974, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>Caffebene USA is looking for a Franchise Sales Manager to head the franchise sales efforts in the Chinese American Market.</p>\n<p>Caffe Bene is the leading coffee franchise chain from South Korea. Established in 2008, we have grown to over 1,300 stores all over the world. Entering the US market in 2012, we have opened in 10 American stores, with 20 more to be opened within this year. With our exquisite interior design, healthy diverse menu, and organized business operations system, we distinguish ourselves from our competitors and create a trendy environment of comfort and relaxation.</p>\n<p>Currently, we are looking for a Sales Manager to manage the Chinese team at our NYC headquarters.</p>\n<p>Main duties and responsibilities will include but not limited to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pitching our company and franchise opportunity to potential Chinese clients</li>\n<li>Building and maintaining trustful relationships with clients</li>\n<li>Following up with clients in a timely manner</li>\n<li>Travelling and working at different franchise shows and seminars</li>\n<li>Coming up with creative ideas for Chinese advertising</li>\n<li>Effectively manage the Chinese sales team</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Education and Experience required:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bachelors Degree</li>\n<li>3 years minimum of previous sales experience</li>\n<li>Experience in managing others</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Skills and abilities required:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fluency in Mandarin Chinese (speaking, reading, writing)</strong></li>\n<li>The candidate must be able to work independently</li>\n<li>Be able to multitask</li>\n<li>Ability to communicate verbally, and understand and follow written and verbal instructions</li>\n<li>Team player who can work well with different personalities</li>\n<li>Ability to work and adapt in an Asian cultural work environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All interested candidates please respond. We are looking to hire as soon as possible.</p>\n<p>Compensation: Based on Experience</p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=88db95f3dca6e5d0', '', 5, 139, 2),
