 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Proven track record in office management and executive administration</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Proactive, self-starter who possesses a friendly, upbeat professional demeanor and keeps a level head</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Detail-oriented individual with exceptional oral/written communication and organizational skills</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Ability to manage multiple tasks and responsibilities simultaneously with minimal supervision</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Experience coordinating international travel</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Experience working in Accounts Payable and other financial functions</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: ''Segoe UI Semibold'', SegoeUI-Bold, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #292929; background-color: transparent;">Fluent in Mandarin Chinese preferred</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: ''Segoe UI'', SegoeUI, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20.799999237060547px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #666666; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: ''Segoe UI Semibold'', SegoeUI-Bold, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: #292929; background-color: transparent;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<h3 style="margin: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-family: ''Segoe UI Semibold'', SegoeUI-Bold, ''Segoe UI'', SegoeUI, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important; color: #333333 !important; font-size: 15px !important; padding: 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: 1.4; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">What will my day to day activities look like?</h3>\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: ''Segoe UI'', SegoeUI, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20.799999237060547px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: #666666; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;">\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Assist the General Manager, Sales Manager and Delivery leadership teams as needed</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Manage front desk reception including the greeting of all visitors</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Receive, verify and file invoices and requisitions for goods and services. Identify errors or discrepancies and resolve before processing. Ongoing maintain and update the list of recurrent Accounts payable items.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Research and resolve any outstanding balances on accounts, including telephone, mail, or email communications with vendors</li>\n<li style="