inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Must be very comfortable with numbers (a math whiz would be great), finances, extremely detail oriented, patient and very adept at Excel spreadsheets and Outlook.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Experience with accounts payable and receivable, writing checks and making electronic payments, processing invoices and statements, coding, expense tracking, and maintaining accounting records.</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc;">Computer proficient, specifically in Microsoft Office Suite, including Excel, Word, SharePoint, One Note, PowerPoint, and Outlook</li>\n</ul>', 'http://www.catapultsystems.com/careers/job-opportunities/Pages/Office-Manager.aspx?location=Seattle%2fRedmond%2c+WA', '', 5, 124, 2),
(331, 1396987950, ' Office Assistant Job Opportunity in Jersey City', 'Xtratech LLC', 'Service', 'Jersey City, NJ, United States', 'United States', 'New Jersey', 'Jersey City', 40.728157, -74.077644, '', '', '', 'H1B', 'Full Time', '<p>Jersey City, NJ</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>H1b</p>\n<p><br />OPT<br /><br /> <br /> xtratechllc@gmail.com</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br />Xtratech LLC is a registered Corporation in the State of New Jersey , we are<br />looking for a diligent, responsible and well-communicating person to finish<br />jobs in a office-based customer representative work.<br />The working place is near Journal Square Path Plaza (10 minutes walk)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This job starts now.<br />We are able support H1b after 1 year of work based on working performance.<br />Job Description:<br />Retail Advertising and Order Processing<br />Wholesale order Bookkeeping and Record<br />Shipping Label printing<br />Use Company Designed Trade Management System<br />Item Stock Fulfillment and Verification<br />Item Purchasing with company funds.</p>\n<p>Requirements:<br />Commitment of working 1 year or longer.<br />Bachelor or higher degree, Business associated educational ground preferred.<br />Fluent in spoken English, good at English in writing, be able to read, <br />understand and respond to clients communications.<br />Good Skills in Microsoft Office and Google Online Docs. Knowledge of <br />Microsoft Sharepoint Designer(Frontpage), Photoshop and Acrobat Professional<br />considered Plus.<br />Be able to work on time (11:00-5:30 daily).</p>\n<p>Please send in brief introduction of yourself: Direct Contact (Phone Number AND Email) Where are you located and what is your planned working schedule.Brief introduction about yourself including WHY you are suitable for this job.<br />Please send the information to our Email at xtratechllc@gmail.com. We will contact you based on job availability.</p>', '', 'xtratechllc@gmail.com', 426, 209, 2);
