(336, 1397109624, ' Dealers Assistant', 'Pace Gallery', 'Service', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.714352, -74.005974, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>Pace Gallery is seeking a Dealer&rsquo;s Assistant to directly support a Director by managing all communication, administrative tasks, handling all pre- and post-sales and exhibition-related activities.<br /><br />Responsibilities <br /><br />&bull; Provide all administrative and personal support to Dealer.<br />&bull; Manage all incoming calls and correspondance<br />&bull; Maintain and organize daily schedule<br />&bull; Serve as a liaison to artists and clients <br />&bull; Work closely with Registrar for all sales, consignments, loans and exhibition-related activities including arranging client viewings handling pre- and post-sales activities. <br /><br />Qualifications<br /><br />&bull; BA Degree required, Art History or related degree. <br />&bull; 2-3 years&rsquo; experience within the art world.<br />&bull; <strong>Fluent in MANDARIN</strong><br />&bull; Must have strong knowledge of the gallery world and of modern and contemporary art.<br />&bull; Must be extremely well presented, polished, professional and articulate. <br />&bull; Must have ability to effectively interact with and gain the confidence of clients, artists and internal staff.<br />&bull; Strong computer skills including Microsoft Word, Excel, Outlook.</p>', '', 'jobs@pacegallery.com', 5, 141, 2),
