le="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Maintain website, including updating content</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n<td class="TDRegular" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 4px 4px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: middle; text-align: left; float: none !important; color: black;" colspan="3" align="left" width="10%">REQUIREMENTS:</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n<td class="TDRegular" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: middle; text-align: left; float: none !important; color: black; background-color: #ffffff; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" colspan="3">&bull; A Master''s degree in China Studies, International Studies, or a related field, and two years'' relevant work experience.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; Excellent written and verbal communication skills.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&bull; <strong>Fluency in speaking and reading Chinese (Mandarin and/or Cantonese preferred).&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></strong><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" />\n<p style="margin: 