(363, 1397846265, '', 'Diamond Wireless (Verizon dealer)', 'Marketing', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.714352, -74.005974, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Description&nbsp;</strong></span></div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">Diamond Wireless has been in business since 1999, and in just over a decade, we&rsquo;ve grown into one of the largest&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">Verizon Wireless dealers in the United States! Through competitive pricing, exceptional customer service and&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">ongoing professional training and support, we&rsquo;ve enjoyed unprecedented sales figures and continuous growth.&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">Currently, due to our expansion efforts, we are seeking outgoing, self-motivated Wireless Sales Consultants to&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">provide excellent care and support to our customers. While this role focuses primarily on sales and exceeding&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">performance goals, the Wireless Consultant will also concentrate on service, ensuring that each customer is listened&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">to, respected, and ultimately satisfied! You will also have several operational responsibilities which require good&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">time-management and organizational skills. If you are a strong communicator with great work ethic and an irresistible personality, then a Sales position with Diamond Wireless may be the right opportunity for you!&nbsp;</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">Diamond Wireless has an exceptional training program designed to teach you about our industry, our products, and&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">most importantly: how to sell them! The knowledge and skills you acquire in our comprehensive, ongoing training&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">program can also be utilized from a management standpoint, as we always strive to promote our managerial staff&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">from within. We are also proud to offer our Wireless Sales Consultants competitive commissions, exciting&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">incentives and lucrative bonuses in return for their dedicated service. You will also receive a great benefits package&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">which includes:</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 1.5em 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Health Insurance</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Dental Coverage</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">401(k) Retirement Planning&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Ample Advancement Opportunities&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Flexible Work Schedules&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Vacation Getaway Rewards&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Training &ndash; become a true sales professional!&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">And MORE!&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Join Our Family! Apply Today!</strong></div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Job Responsibilities</strong></div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">As a Wireless Sales Consultant for Diamond, you will sell and service both new and existing Verizon customers &ndash;&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">ensuring that their needs are met and that our standards of operation are consistently upheld. This role is truly that of&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">a consultant, as you will be offering service support as well as technical assistance, as needed.</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">&nbsp;Additional responsibilities for the Wireless Sales Consultant include:</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 1.5em 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Keeping the store clean and organized&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Ensuring that merchandise is fully stocked&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Assisting with returns, exchanges, etc.&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Performing inventory counts&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Managing the cash drawer&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Preparing bank deposits&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><strong style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">Requirements&nbsp;</strong></div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">As a Wireless Sales Consultant for Diamond Wireless, you must stay abreast of new technological developments in</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">the industry. You must also be computer literate, understanding how to run Windows applications, navigate the&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">internet and efficiently use Microsoft Office programs. POS System experience is a plus.</div>\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">Additional requirements of the Wireless Sales Consultant include:</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 1.5em 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; color: #111111; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;">\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">High School diploma; some college experience, a plus&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Ability to stand for extended periods of time&nbsp;</li>\n<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong>Bilingual Mandarin</strong></li>\n</ul>', 'http://newton.newtonsoftware.com/career/JobIntroduction.action?id=8a5814f644f21364014500704a6e339a', '', 5, 159, 2);
