(365, 1397860419, 'Customer Service Specialist and Sales & Marketing Support', 'Prince of Peace Enterprises', 'Marketing', 'Hayward, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Hayward', 37.668819, -122.080795, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>We have an immediate opportunity for an ambitious, energetic and positive individual.&nbsp;<br />We are looking for a customer service specialist that will also support some aspects of Sales &amp; Marketing.&nbsp;<br /><strong>Overview/Responsibilities:</strong>&nbsp;As a CSS you will be responsible for all customer service duties that include but are not limited to: responding to phone &amp; email inquiries, resolving customer complaints, order entry, invoicing, some logistics, and provide support to the sales &amp; marketing teams.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Qualifications:</strong><br />Must sustain a sense of urgency, strong commitment, and have great accountability to fulfill this position&nbsp;<br />Must be able to work in a fast pace working environment&nbsp;<br />Excellent communication, organizational, and time management skills&nbsp;<br />Ability to build and maintain all customer relationships&nbsp;<br />Ability to work in a team environment as well as independently&nbsp;<br />Good problem solving and time management skills&nbsp;<br />3 plus years experience&nbsp;<br />Proficient at Microsoft Office (Excel, Word, Outlook, etc.)&nbsp;<br />Must be able to travel 7-10 days per year (tradeshow attendance)&nbsp;<br />Knowledge of EDI &amp; logistic experience is a plus&nbsp;<br />Bilingual (Mandarin/Cantonese) is a plus&nbsp;<br />Company offers a competitive salary and benefit package that includes medical, dental and vision insurance, 401K plan, vacation time and paid holidays. Salary will be determined by your experience and skills.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Please send resume to:</strong></p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/rc/clk?jk=a8fde38241b2713b&from=vj&grandfrom=ja&tk=18lq0tei3069g5pn&pos=bottom', '', 44, 158, 2),
