(675, 1410137105, '', 'Everest International Education', 'Language', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class="snip">\n<p>A prestigious private international high school in Beijing, China urgently needs two English teachers to teach English language, literature, reading, and composition for 10th-12th grade. Up to 25 hours of instruction per week, as well as English corner, office hours, night classes, no more than two nights a week. Maximum class size of 25.</p>\n<p>Minimum Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree</li>\n<li>native speaker of English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Preferred:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>M.A. or higher in Language, Education, or related area</li>\n<li>3+ years&rsquo; experience</li>\n<li>TEFL, TESOL, ESL, Teaching License, or Teaching abroad experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Compensation</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$1,625-$3,250 per month ($19,500-$39,000 per year), at current exchange rate, DOE</li>\n<li>Holiday bonus</li>\n<li>Round-trip plane tickets from Beijing to home country, max $2000 per contract year</li>\n<li>Sponsored work Visa</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Benefits</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Paid vacations over winter and summer break</li>\n<li>Vacations on Christmas and Chinese holidays</li>\n<li>School provides furnished apartment with shared living room &ndash; ten minute walk to campus</li>\n<li>Social insurance and accident insurance</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Everest International Education is your advocate for teaching abroad. We provide you with ongoing support and cultural assistance throughout your teaching assignment &ndash; all FREE of charge.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/Everest-International-Education/jobs/English-Teacher-c4c8a9de67f01583', '', 980, 126, 2),
(676, 1410277848, ' Office Assistant Job Opportunity in Jersey City', 'Xtratech LLC', 'Marketing', 'Jersey City, NJ, United States', 'United States', 'New Jersey', 'Jersey City', 40.728157, -74.077644, '', '', '', 'H1B', 'Internship', '<p><br />Jersey City, NJ<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />OPT<br /><br /> <br />&nbsp;xtratechllc@gmail.com<br /><br /><img src="http://www.nychinaren.com/images/forum/large/6711__16202_96711.jpg" alt="" /><br /><br /><br />Xtratech LLC is a registered Corporation in the State of New Jersey , we are<br />looking for a diligent, responsible and well-communicating person to finish<br />jobs in a office-based customer representative work.<br />The working place is near Journal Square Path Plaza (10 minutes walk)<br /><img src="http://i1160.photobucket.com/albums/q481/eucapb/Untitled-1_zps39552b55.jpg" alt="" width="597" /><br /><br /><br />This job starts at the beginning of Feburary.<br />We are able support H1b after 1 year of work based on working performance.<br />Job Description:<br />Retail Advertising and Order Processing<br />Wholesale order Bookkeeping and Record<br />Shipping Label printing<br />Use Company Designed Trade Management System<br />Item Stock Fulfillment and Verification<br />Item Purchasing with company funds.<br /><br />Requirements:<br />Commitment of working 1 year or longer.<br />Bachelor or higher degree, Business associated educational ground preferred.<br />Fluent in spoken English, good at English in writing, be able to read,&nbsp;<br />understand and respond to clients communications.<br />Good Skills in Microsoft Office and Google Online Docs. Knowledge of&nbsp;<br />Microsoft Sharepoint Designer(Frontpage), Photoshop and Acrobat Professional<br />considered Plus.<br />Be able to work on time (11:00-5:30 daily).<br /><br />Please send in brief introduction of yourself:<br />Direct Contact (Phone Number AND Email)<br />Where are you located and what is your planned working schedule.<br />Brief introduction about yourself including WHY you are suitable for this&nbsp;<br />job.<br />Please send the information to our Email at&nbsp;ongoing@gmail.com.&nbsp;We will&nbsp;<br />contact you based on job availability.<br /><br /><br /><br /></p>', 'http://www.mitbbs.com/article_t/JobMarket/31209799.html', 'ongoing@gmail.com', 1147, 228, 2),
(677, 1410291519, '', 'HSBC', 'Management', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<div id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1598.row1" class="contentlinepanel" title="">\n<div><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Processes and initiates various financial transactions for Company customers and assists branch office management in new business through referrals and meets established sales referral and promotional sales goals. Enhances Company image through pro-active customer-driven servicing of their needs in support of the goal of exceeding customer expectations.</span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>Principal Accountabilities: Key activities and decision making areas</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><strong>Impact on the Business</strong></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Meet established sales referral and promotional sales goals</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Accept and process deposits, payments, checks for cashing and other transactions according to established procedures and performance standards.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Ready workstation at start of shift; strike and balance cash and transactions at end of shift.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Live and represent the brand; exemplify the five brand attributes of being perceptive, progressive, responsive, respectful and fair, both internally and externally.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div><strong>Customers / Stakeholders</strong></div>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Enhance Company image through pro-active customer-driven servicing of their needs in support of the goal of exceeding customer expectations; initiate referral of new business through customer contact and use of customer relationship management system</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div><strong>Leadership &amp; Teamwork</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><strong>Operational Effectiveness &amp; Control</strong></div>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Adhere to branch cash control and security requirements in control of cash and negotiable items.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Adhere to established customer interaction standards for every transaction.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Maintain current knowledge of Company products and services and applicable Federal regulations, including Bank Secrecy and Know Your Customer principles. Adhere strictly to compliance and operational risk controls in accordance with Company and regulatory standards, policies and practices; report control weaknesses, compliance breaches and operational loss events.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">To implement the Group compliance policy locally by containing compliance risk in liaison with the Head of Group Compliance, Global Business Compliance Officer, Area Compliance Officer or Local Compliance Officer, ensuring adequate compliance resources and training, fostering a compliance culture and optimizing relations with regulators.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Complete other responsibilities, as assigned.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><strong>Major Challenges</strong><em>&nbsp;(The challenges inherent in the role that require a continual test of the role holder&rsquo;s abilities)</em></span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><strong>Role Context</strong>&nbsp;<em>(The environment and operating conditions of the role including the extent of guidance and authority)</em></span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><strong>Management of Risk</strong>&nbsp;<em>(Operational Risk / FIM requirements)</em></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Ensure compliance, operational risk controls in accordance with HSBC or regulatory standards and policies; and optimize relations with regulators by addressing any issues.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><strong>Observation of Internal Controls</strong><em>&nbsp;(Compliance Policy / FIM requirements)</em></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Maintains HSBC internal control standards, including timely implementation of internal and external audit points together with any issues raised by external regulators.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<span class="blockpanel"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1656.row1" class="contentlinepanel" title="">\n<div id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1672.row1" class="inlinepanel" title=""><span class="subtitle">Qualifications</span></div>\n<span class="blockpanel"><span>&nbsp;</span></span>\n<div><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><strong>Knowledge &amp; Experience / Qualifications</strong>&nbsp;<em>(For the role &ndash; not the role holder. Minimum requirements of the role.)</em></span></div>\n<span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Must be fluent in English and Chinese (Cantonese or Mandarin)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Minimum of one year&rsquo;s proven customer service and/or sales experience or equivalent, including cash handling experience.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Minimum of high school diploma or equivalent experience.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Demonstrated interpersonal, communication and analytical skills.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Proficiency with personal computers as well as pertinent mainframe systems and software packages.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Positive customer service attributes.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-family: Verdana;">Demonstrated proficiency with sales referrals and product knowledge.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-family: Verdana;">EEO/AA/Minorities/Women/Disability/Veterans</span></p>\n<span class="blockpanel"><span>&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1714.row1" class="contentlinepanel" title="">\n<h2 class="no-change-header-inline"><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1730.row1" class="subtitle" title="">Job Field</span></h2>\n<span class="inline">&nbsp;</span><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1751.row1" class="subtitle" title="">:</span><span class="inline">&nbsp;</span><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1761.row1" class="text" title="">Customer Service</span></div>\n<div id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1768.row1" class="contentlinepanel" title="">\n<h2 class="no-change-header-inline"><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1784.row1" class="subtitle" title="">Primary Location</span></h2>\n<span class="inline">&nbsp;</span><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1805.row1" class="subtitle" title="">:</span><span class="inline">&nbsp;</span><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1815.row1" class="text" title="">North America-United States-New York-Brooklyn</span></div>\n<div id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1876.row1" class="contentlinepanel" title="">\n<h2 class="no-change-header-inline"><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1892.row1" class="subtitle" title="">Schedule</span></h2>\n<span class="inline">&nbsp;</span><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1913.row1" class="subtitle" title="">:</span><span class="inline">&nbsp;</span><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1923.row1" class="jobtype" title="">Part-time</span><span class="inline">&nbsp;</span>\n<h2 class="no-change-header-inline"><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1946.row1" class="subtitle" title="">Shift</span></h2>\n<span class="inline">&nbsp;</span><span id="requisitionDescriptionInterface.ID1967.row1