(678, 1410291709, '', 'Transportation/Logistics', 'Finance', 'Industry, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'City of Industry', 34.019733, -117.958672, '', '', '', 'None', 'Part Time', '<p>Duties including but not limited to:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Maintenance of A/R files and customer records</li>\n<li>Maintenance of customer records in various operation systems</li>\n<li>Review and reconciliation of customer transactions between accounting system vs. operation system</li>\n<li>Review customer aging on a daily/weekly basis</li>\n<li>Make daily collection calls, send statement to outstanding customers, interact to resolve issues</li>\n<li>Strong follow-up, collection and allocation of payments</li>\n<li>File small claims for collection</li>\n<li>Review cash receipts for accuracy</li>\n<li>Review contracts and research all customer disputes</li>\n<li>Reconcile Customer Accounts</li>\n<li>Team player, working with multiple locations, facility managers and staff</li>\n<li>Develop SOP and work flow</li>\n<li>Strong excel skills to develop various analysis</li>\n<li>Weekly cash forecast in timely manner and accurately</li>\n<li>Posting of all credit account payments received</li>\n<li>Able to process month end A/P and A/R</li>\n<li>Perform other duties as assigned</li>\n<li>Managerial skills a plus</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BA degree in Accounting/Finance</li>\n<li>3-5 years hands on experience</li>\n<li>Solids understanding of GAAP and standard operating procedures</li>\n<li>Strong computer and communication skills</li>\n<li>Bi-lingual in Chinese</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Experience in a transportation or logistics company and or with Great Plains is a plus</p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/viewjob?cmp=Logistics-Team-%2F-SB-Freight&t=Senior+Accountant&jk=85bae059bb3c10d2&sjdu=QwrRXKrqZ3CNX5W-O9jEvUUdXQhhKNOAMcM5flKILog0luRRK07Q2JBCFU-YI1RQlFSHxPinA8xvO0EpqjkCXw', '', 980, 125, 2);
