(679, 1410376989, '', 'MIRAMAX', 'Entertainment', 'Santa Monica, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Santa Monica', 34.019455, -118.491188, '', '', '', 'None', 'Internship', '<div class="section_head clearfix">\n<h3>Position Summary</h3>\n</div>\n<p>The Human Resources group provides ongoing support to our employees in a myriad of ways. The intern will be exposed to various Human Resources functions such as full-cycle recruitment, on-boarding, records management, and employee/intern engagement activities. The ideal candidate is an aspiring HR professional and has the ability to maintain a strict code of confidentiality and discretion.</p>\n<div class="section_head clearfix">\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Emphasized support to Miramax recruitment efforts for open positions and year round internship program. Including but not limited to, posting positions on various career/school sites, sort &amp; screen resumes, screen applications, check references, and schedule interviews</li>\n<li>Create New Hire, Benefits &amp; 401K, and New Intern packets, ensuring forms are updated and available</li>\n<li>Assist with Employee Relations, involved with the planning and execution of events</li>\n<li>Provide social media insights for Employer Branding strategy</li>\n<li>Research HR best practices and give recommendations to HR on a case-by-case basis</li>\n<li>Other special projects as needed</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="section_head clearfix">\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>In pursuit of a Bachelor or Graduate degree at an approved Accredited Institution and must be able to provide documentation to confirm progress</li>\n<li>Junior/Senior students desired with major in: Business, Human Resources, Psychology, Communications, or related</li>\n<li>Ideal student will be interested in a career in Human Resources</li>\n<li>Strong attention to detail, good follow through skills, great communication and multi-tasking skills</li>\n<li>Can-do attitude with a strong sense of customer service and confidentiality</li>\n<li>Thrives in an entrepreneurial fast paced environment and can wear many different hats as needed</li>\n<li>Proficient in Microsoft Office Suite &amp; Internet savvy</li>\n<li>Basic knowledge and understanding of social media</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="section_head clearfix">\n<h3>Preferred</h3>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Previous internship experience in field</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="section_head clearfix">\n<h3>Perks at Miramax</h3>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Ability to get hands-on experience from an industry leader</li>\n<li>Opportunity to network with key executives in the business</li>\n<li>Free Lunch Fridays!</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="section_head clearfix">&nbsp;</div>', '', 'internships@miramax.com', 980, 153, 2),
