(708, 1411615880, 'Health & Beauty Consultant and online franchise expending ', 'Health&Beauty ', 'Marketing', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '', '', '', 'None', 'Part Time', '<p>Looking for business minded entrepreneurs to help bring a well established product brokerage and Internet marketing company to New York Area!</p>\n<p>This is an independent partnership and earnings are relative to your willingness to follow a proven franchise business plan and put the time in. If you are looking for a get rich quick scheme, this is not it. However, If you are looking to own your own business part time (8-15 hour/week) or simply supplement your already full time income and are good with health and beauty industry (especially with Chinese herb or pharmaceutical background), this could be the perfect fit for you!</p>\n<p>Please respond by email to schedule an appointment, also respond with your biography via PHONE contact.<br /><br />**Due to internet scam issues, we do not discuss or provide any information over the e-mail or phone.</p>\n<p>Contact Email: healthbeauty2015@gmail.com&nbsp;</p>', '', '', 1195, 137, 2),
