(711, 1411793232, '', '', 'Management', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<h1>BI-LINGUAL MANDARIN CHINESE-MARKET MARKETING MANAGER </h1>\n<h2>About the Job</h2>\n<div id="jobBodyContent">\n<p><strong>KOREA GINSENG CORPORATION</strong></p>\n<p><strong><br />(www.kgcus.com)<br /><br /></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><br />(www.kgcus.com)</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>BI-LINGUAL MANDARIN CHINESE-MARKET MARKETING MANAGER<br /><br /></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>-- Must be&nbsp;Fluent in Business-Level Mandarin (AND either English or Korean) &ndash;<br />(CERRITOS, CA)&nbsp;&nbsp;Full-Time - Monthly Salary: $3,000-4,000/month (Depending on Experience)</strong><br />Small corporate office with&nbsp;national U.S. business&nbsp;is looking for someone to help us strategically develop the U.S. Chinese American markets for Korean ginseng consumption.&nbsp; You must be experienced with US Chinese health food channels (US Vietnamese or American Mainstream also considered).&nbsp;Pay depends on experience --we are looking for the right person, considering full background.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN">&mdash;&mdash;</span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>CERRITOS,CA<span lang="ZH-CN"></span>-<span lang="ZH-CN"></span>$3,000-$4,000<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>USE of EXCEL and OFFICE SOFTWARE/ABILITY TO MAKE DETAILED REPORTS REQUIRED&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>EXCEL&nbsp;<span lang="ZH-CN"></span>OFFICE<span lang="ZH-CN"></span>/<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">More information:<br /></span>Korean Ginseng company wants to hire: Marketing assistant fluent in Mandarin + English or Korean (ability in Cantonese also desirable, but Mandarin is required).&nbsp; Greater consideration will be given to candidates with MARKETING degrees and/or candidates with&nbsp;significant management experience in US-Chinese/US-Mainstream wholesale distribution channels&nbsp;(this is not overseas business, but ability to communicate professionally in a multi-ethnic environment is required).&nbsp; Experience with ginseng, herbal and dietary supplement markets is especially desired, but other health and beauty products will be considered.<br />Must be able to communicate professionally in business Mandarin, make detailed Marketing reports, using professional analysis (4Ps, SWAT, etc), using evidence generated through research or third-parties.&nbsp; The ability to conceptualize the new products development and bring to market new products is helpful.&nbsp; Experience managing buyer accounts is helpful.&nbsp; Knowledge of food industry norms, pricing structures, and channel-distribution logic strongly desired.</p>\n<p><br /><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>MARKETING<span lang="ZH-CN"></span>4Ps,SWAT<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Responsibilities:</span>&nbsp;<br />Develop &amp; pioneer the U.S. Chinese and other ethnic markets by expanding &amp; managing sales/buyer channels for ginseng products within the Chinese-American&nbsp;food/drink markets, other U.S. Asian markets and U.S. mainstream.&nbsp; Must maintain professional Marketing skills,&nbsp;have the ability to learn quickly, have sincerity and act to generate creative solutions to complex problems.&nbsp; Fluency in Chinese characters/business writing and TYPING are required for generation of copy-write content for PR releases, articles, advertisements and product overviews.&nbsp; Must be capable of working across fields to maximize corporate outcomes.&nbsp; Data-analysis, reports-generation, account monitoring, trade-shows, demo management, research, some light travel, problem solving&nbsp;and proper business etiquette within are required.&nbsp;&nbsp;Must have the ability to work on practical day-to-day level sales growth, while simultaneously increasing the company''s knowledge and capability, building complexity and recommending budgets through ROI analysis.&nbsp;&nbsp;Employee will be expected to develop professional logic and evidence based business growth plans and implementing them, as approved by the Branch Manager.&nbsp; Travel may be required, including National (CA-NY), and local (LA/Irvine, etc); however work will primarily be in the Cerritos, CA main office and work travel is compensated.<br /><br /></p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>/<span lang="ZH-CN"></span>ROI<span lang="ZH-CN">&mdash;&mdash;</span>Cerritos<span lang="ZH-CN"></span>&nbsp;<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Benefits:</span><br />Salary, health/dental &amp; possible performance bonuses, following 3-month introductory period.<br /><br /></p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>/<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Notice:</span><br />Background checks will be conducted &amp; eligibility to work will be verified.<br /><br /></p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></span><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>TO APPLY -- PLEASE FOLLOW THESE DIRECTIONS:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />Send resume &amp; introductory cover-letter.&nbsp; Your cover-letter must describe why you think your experience makes you a good fit for this position.&nbsp; Your cover-letter should be send in English AND Chinese (both) to demonstrate your language/typing ability.&nbsp; Send to:&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;">kgc.usa@gmail.com</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;">kgc.usa@gmail.com</span>&nbsp;<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>--- Must be&nbsp;Fluent in Mandarin (and also either Korean or English) ---<br /></strong><br />KGC North America:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.kgcus.com/">www.kgcus.com</a></p>\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>Salary</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>USD 3000 - 4000 Per Month DOE</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>Career Level Required</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Experienced (Non-Manager)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>Experience Required</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>4+ Years</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>Education Required</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Bachelor''s Degree (Marketing or Related)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>Job Type</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Employee</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>Job Status</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Full Time<br /><br /><br /></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.kgcus.com/">www.kgcus.com</a></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; $3000-$4000<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span lang="ZH-CN"></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span lang="ZH-CN"></span></p>\n</div>', 'http://jobview.monster.com/BI-LINGUAL-MANDARIN-CHINESE-MARKET-MARKETING-MANAGER--Job-CERRITOS-CA-US-139357699.aspx?WT.mc_n=Indeed_US&from=indeed', 'kgc.usa@gmail.com', 980, 193, 2),
(712, 1411850404, '', 'International Business Promotion, Inc. (IBP, Inc.)', 'Marketing', 'Jersey City, NJ, United States', 'United States', 'New Jersey', 'Jersey City', 40.728157, -74.077644, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<p>Our client is a Japanese company which has a number of offices through the US. It is currently looking for a sales professional who could assist its clients in New Jersey Office. As Sales Representative, you will be responsible for communicating with new and existing clients.</p>\n<p>Minimum requirements: - At least 3 years of sales experience to be qualified.<br />- English: Business level. Chinese: Native level.<br />- AA degree or higher education preferred.<br />- Authorized to work in the US.<br />- Valid US driver&rsquo;s license.<br />- Computer skills in Microsoft Office.<br />- Willing to travel for business.<br />- Detail-oriented.<br />- Great communication skills.<br />- Team player.<br />- Able to start immediately.</p>\n<p>Compensation: $35,000</p>\n<p>--------------------------------------------------<br />International Business Promotion, Inc. (IBP, Inc.)<br />1601 Broadway 12th Floor<br />New York, NY 10019 USA</p>\n<p>Website: www.ibp-nyc.com</p>\n<p>International Business Promotion, Inc. (IBP, Inc.) is an international recruiting and marketing company, headquartered at Times Square in New York City. For the recruiting business, we are specializing in the Japanese-English bilingual candidates throughout the US. In addition to the recruiting business, we provide a wide scope of marketing services to help Japanese companies expand their businesses in the US. We also help American companies enter into the Japanese market.</p>\n<p>Job Type: Full-time</p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/viewjob?cmp=International-Business-Promotion,-Inc.-(IBP,-Inc.)&t=Sales+Representative&jk=770e1cdf3931ce5a&sjdu=QwrRXKrqZ3CNX5W-O9jEvdWaFExGg97Dg5JRAWGCkoBPsgPD0HVUZX-ctWMTFdcA-y5W9XQSdVmCyTnRhAYDOQYtEpKVYQ0zo3BfOGSFjVU', '', 980, 117, 2),
(713, 1411878800, 'Production Manager (Mandarin Speaking Only)', 'Victoria Classics', 'Management', 'New York, NY, United States', 'United States', 'New York', 'New York', 40.712784, -74.005943, '', '', '', 'None', 'Full Time', '<h2>About the Job</h2>\n<div id="jobBodyContent">\n<p><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;">Production Manager (Mandarin Speaking Only)</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><br />Victoria Classics is a major importer of fashionable home textile products. We specialize in highly embellished and hand crafted product, designed to meet the individual needs of each customer.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;">Victoria Classics is proud of its diverse customer base that spans many diverse operations. From department stores and big box retailers to discounters and alternative marketers.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;">Since being founded over 26 years ago, Victoria Classics has grown into one of the most successful companies in its field nationwide.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;">Please visit our Website,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.victoriaclassics.com/">www.victoriaclassics.com</a>&nbsp;for more information about our Company.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;">We are currently searching for a&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;">Production Manager</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;for our busy Edison, New Jersey Headquarters. Home Textile Experience is&nbsp;<strong>preferred.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;">Required Job Skills:</span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Experience with Merchandising and Product Development required.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;">Must speak, read and write fluent Mandarin.&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;Must have experience with&nbsp;<strong>Home Textiles</strong>&nbsp;and must have excellent communication/follow up skills, organizational and administrative skills.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Candidates must be willing to take ownership of their work. Will act as liaison between U.S. Headquarters, China Office and Chinese Factories.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Must be business savvy and able to negotiate.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">They will oversee sample development from start to finish and ensure that delivery schedules are met. They will also work with the Quality Control Department to help ensure standards.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">They will assist in the testing of products.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Should come from a good buying house and be at a Senior Merchant Level.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;</span><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Must be willing to travel to china&nbsp;3 to&nbsp;4 times a year.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n</div>', 'http://jobview.monster.com/Production-Manager-Mandarin-Speaking-Only-Job-Edison-NJ-US-139891177.aspx?WT.mc_n=Indeed_US&from=indeed', '', 980, 188, 2),
