(734, 1413073949, '', 'Biotech Energy Inc', 'Marketing', 'Los Angeles, CA, United States', 'United States', 'California', 'Los Angeles', 34.052235, -118.243683, '', '', '', 'H1B', 'Full Time', '<p>FOR EMPLOYMENT<br />Biotech Energy Inc. is a newly launched company in health industry. We mainly sell functional supplement products combined with our unique music therapy as well as some high tech medical equipment.<br />If you are an organized, decisive, result-oriented personnel with a natural fondness for people, negotiation, and ready markets and channels, we may have a job for you as Sales Manager. We are seeking a highly motivated and outgoing salesperson who possesses a passion to succeed and ambitious career goals. The primary responsibility of this position is to achieve a larger market share, create more brand awareness/loyalty and increase profit margins and marketing experience and connections available .The company offers an excellent benefits package, including health insurance (medical, dental, vision), paid vacation, sick, personal days, 401(k) plan and profit sharing.<br />Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>High energy and good public relation skills</li>\n<li>Enthusiasm and aggressiveness</li>\n<li>Excellent communication skills and marketing experience</li>\n<li>Personal accountability</li>\n<li>Excellent native English and Mandarin Chinese preferably</li>\n<li>Knowledge of the retail and wholesale trade a plus</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Skills:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ability to acquire new business</li>\n<li>Experienced presenter</li>\n<li>Can overcome objections</li>\n<li>Good account and territory management skills</li>\n<li>Excellent follow up skills</li>\n<li>Proficiency in MS Suite</li>\n<li>Knowledge of sales strategies</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Experience:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>5 + years of progressive career sales growth in sales positions</li>\n<li>Selling tangible consumer products</li>\n<li>Previous experience selling to a dealer network is preferred</li>\n<li>Sewing machine industry experience preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Education:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bachelor''s Degree minimum or equivalent experience</li>\n<li>Foreign language and trade diploma or experience</li>\n<li>Rich background in dietary supplements and therapy devices</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/Biotech-Energy-Inc/jobs/Marketing-Manager-e79dee53b16d0328', '', 980, 134, 2),
