ticipates in trade shows and conventions</li>\n<li>Some travels required</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bilingual English/Chinese a plus</li>\n<li>Good communication &amp; customer services skills</li>\n<li>Computer proficiency</li>\n<li>Self-motivated</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>EVA Airways is an Equal Opportunity Employer.</em></p>', 'http://www.indeed.com/cmp/EVA-Airways/jobs/Full-Time-Passenger-Sales-bb669ed06f92ac2b', '', 980, 177, 2),
